**If extend, supplement, or match_style:**

"Please share the existing code you'd like me to reference:

**Options:**
- **Local folder path** - e.g., `/Users/you/projects/my-app` or `~/Documents/my-project`
- **GitHub URL** - e.g., `https://github.com/org/repo` or `github.com/org/repo/tree/branch/folder`
